接管人接收他和家人的物業，結束陳氏家族自1980年代起在此居住的歷史。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;陳秉志在訪問中又表示，該單位自2023年底一直委託放售，惟未能為自住獨立屋成功找到買家，導致物業最終淪為銀主盤的結局。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;薄扶林豪宅淪銀主盤！「磁帶大王」陳秉志自住屋放售叫價4.3億&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.am730.com.hk/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93/%E8%96%84%E6%89%B6%E6%9E%97%E8%87%AA%E4%BD%8F%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85%E6%B7%AA%E9%8A%80%E4%B8%BB%E7%9B%A4-%E7%A3%81%E5%B8%B6%E5%A4%A7%E7%8E%8B-%E9%99%B3%E7%A7%89%E5%BF%97%E5%8F%97%E8%A8%AA-%E6%AC%A0%E5%AF%8C%E9%82%A6%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C3.5%E5%84%84%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE-%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0-/562195" target="_blank" uhash="b18d038319afb72a67a1ca944b903916"&gt;https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/薄扶林自住豪宅淪銀主盤-磁帶大王-陳秉志受訪-欠富邦銀行3.5億貸款-更新-/562195&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31934772&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1570563237682f8b460060b5_69410369"/><published>2025-05-22T11:59:19+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>091488ab129fd8fc7fccf9e5ff0c7dbd</id><title>現在一字頭就可以買。住何文田了</title><updated>2025-05-22T12:26:41+08:00</updated><author><name>edwin8888</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-22T12:26:41+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572513569"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572513569"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16243491" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572513569" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250522/20250522_a74847d8ee520ea3f0d1VREyqIKCTU8a.png"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/f1580d/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250522/20250522_a74847d8ee520ea3f0d1VREyqIKCTU8a.png"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div c